      "[000002.44]  01-19 00:43  CutskyHOD                    INFO     Load existing hod instead of generating new ones.\n",
      "[000002.44]  01-19 00:43  CutskyHOD                    INFO     Processing snapshot at z = 0.5 for redshift range (0.4, 0.6)\n",
      "[000019.16]  01-19 00:44  CutskyHOD                    INFO     Applying RSD.\n",
      "[000064.85]  01-19 00:44  CutskyHOD                    INFO     Applying angular mask.\n",
